official_title: A bill to amend the Farm Labor Contractor Registration Act of 1963 to exempt contractors of workers engaged in custom cutting or combine operations in connection with the harvesting of grains.

summary.text: States that the term "migrant worker" under the Farm Labor Contractor Act of 1963 shall not include any individual whose primary employment is in custom cutting or combine operations in connection with the harvesting of grains.
